      <div class="space-y-6 my-10">
        <details class="bg-surface-variant/30 border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-xl p-5 cursor-pointer hover:bg-surface-variant/50 transition-colors">
          <summary class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface">How do I choose between single-wall and double-wall corrugated sheets?</summary>
          <p class="font-body text-secondary mt-3 leading-relaxed">Single-wall sheets (one fluted layer) work well for light to moderate protection and cost-sensitive applications. Double-wall sheets (two fluted layers) provide premium protection for heavy items, fragile goods, or items that must survive long-distance shipping. Consider your product weight and value to determine the best choice. Our team can recommend the optimal configuration.</p>
