        <details class="bg-surface-variant/30 border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-xl p-5 cursor-pointer hover:bg-surface-variant/50 transition-colors">
          <summary class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface">How are corrugated sheets typically cut or formed?</summary>
          <p class="font-body text-secondary mt-3 leading-relaxed">Corrugated sheets can be cut using sharp utility knives for simple straight cuts, or custom-cut using industrial cutting equipment for complex shapes and patterns. Most businesses use basic hand tools for on-site customization, while larger operations use precision cutting machinery. Quinocycle can provide pre-cut sheets to your specifications.</p>
