        <details class="bg-surface-variant/30 border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-xl p-5 cursor-pointer hover:bg-surface-variant/50 transition-colors">
          <summary class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface">What is the shelf life of corrugated cardboard sheets?</summary>
          <p class="font-body text-secondary mt-3 leading-relaxed">Corrugated sheets maintain quality indefinitely when stored in dry conditions. Moisture is the primary concern—store sheets in dry environments away from moisture and humidity. Properly stored corrugated sheets can be used for years without degradation. We recommend maintaining inventory in climate-controlled storage areas.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-surface-variant/30 border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-xl p-5 cursor-pointer hover:bg-surface-variant/50 transition-colors">
